text: Easy to miss. Very underrated church. Try their service if you are old school, family oriented
Wonderful Sunday services with the first at 8.30am. Sunday school at 9.45am and main service at 11.00am. New visitors are received and treated well.
The Church of Jesus Christ is a church worth going to.  thank God、God bless💖🌈
